@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<section class="privacy-policy container-fluid my-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-primary">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>Welcome to our Library System! We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information while you enjoy exploring and borrowing books online.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>To provide a seamless experience, we collect the following information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Account details:</strong> Your name, email, and login credentials.</li>
        <li><strong>Borrowing activity:</strong> The books you borrow, return dates, and preferences to personalize recommendations.</li>
        <li><strong>Device & usage data:</strong> Information about how you access and use our platform to improve functionality.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-5">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>We use your data to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Manage your account and borrowing activities.</li>
        <li>Personalize book recommendations tailored to your interests.</li>
        <li>Send important notifications about due dates and library updates.</li>
        <li>Continuously improve our website and services.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-5">3. Your Privacy Matters</h3>
    <p>We do <strong>NOT</strong> sell or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes. Your information is stored securely with encryption and access controls.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">4. Cookies & Tracking</h3>
    <p>We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience, remember your preferences, and gather anonymous analytics to understand how our library is used. You can manage cookie preferences in your browser settings.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-5">5. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access and update your personal information anytime via your account.</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data if you decide to close your account.</li>
        <li>Opt out of non-essential communications.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-5">6. Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have questions about this policy or your data, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:privacy@librarysystem.com">privacy@librarysystem.com</a>. We’re here to help!</p>

    <hr class="my-5" />

    <p class="text-muted fst-italic small">Thank you for trusting us to be your digital library companion. Happy reading!</p>
</section>
